description: Generate a cinematic AI portrait of yourself or a person, keeping the real face intact. Shot from a low angle for a taller, confident look, the subject wears a dark puffer jacket and modern glasses. Neon yellow-orange lighting with a curved LED streak adds a futuristic urban vibe, highlighting the face and jacket textures. Perfect for moody, stylish portraits with a streetwear and futuristic aesthetic.

AI prompt for an ultra-realistic 8K cinematic portrait, framed 9:16 as an Android wallpaper. A person with an athletic build stands behind an open refrigerator door in a minimarket, misty glass adding condensation, droplets, and neon reflections. Subject is casually stylish, relaxed but confident, with piercing gaze and natural gestures. Warm shop lights mix with cool tones, creating a moody film-photography look.

AI prompt for an ultra-realistic 8K cinematic portrait of a stylish young man crouched confidently next to a rugged black pickup truck in a dark underground parking garage. The subject wears a black leather jacket, black outfit, and sunglasses, holding a spiked metal bat. Moody dramatic lighting, soft shadows, detailed textures, and cyberpunk gangster vibe create a hyper-detailed cinematic shot with DSLR depth of field. The face perfectly matches the uploaded reference.

AI art prompt to create a cinematic studio portrait in 9:16 format with a clean golden gradient background. The subject wears a cream blazer, pastel shirt, tailored trousers, and loafers, posed elegantly on a modern chair. Styled with dramatic lighting, shallow depth of field, and low-angle capture, this prompt emphasizes luxury, detail, and Instagram-viral aesthetics.

An AI prompt to generate a realistic fashion portrait. Creates a cinematic photo of a person in dark oversized streetwear, sitting on a white bean bag against a simple grey background. Perfect for creating stylish personal branding images.

An ultra-realistic cinematic black-and-white portrait prompt. Creates a photo of a man leaning on a vintage car with a Doberman, using IMAX-style 85mm lens and natural lighting for a professional film look.
A fine art photography prompt for a cinematic golden hour portrait. Creates a western-inspired scene of a person with a Porsche 959 in a prairie, using telephoto lens and warm, soft lighting.
AI prompt to generate a dark, cinematic mirror selfie portrait. Creates an image of a person in a Ferrari racing jacket in an elevator, using a reference photo for the face. Fashion editorial style.

AI prompt for an ultra-realistic cinematic portrait of a person on a beige couch holding a vintage portable TV. Features IMAX-style photography, hard flash lighting, shallow depth of field, and a tense expression, rendered with realistic film grain.

AI prompt to generate a cinematic editorial portrait with strong motion blur and slow shutter streaks. Uses your uploaded face to create a high-contrast, dynamic fashion image with an abstract, viral photography style.

AI prompt for an ultra-realistic cinematic portrait shot from behind, showing your reflection in a modern LED-lit mirror. You wear a black outfit, pose introspectively, with high contrast lighting and shallow depth of field.

AI prompt to generate a high-end editorial fashion photo of you as a model. Full-body shot in an oversized beige linen suit, with intense golden backlighting, long shadows on a concrete floor, shot on a professional camera.

AI prompt to create a cinematic, full-body street fashion portrait. Generates a hyper-realistic photo with dramatic lighting, detailed avant-garde clothing like a patchwork sweater and cargo pants, and professional DSLR quality.

AI prompt to generate a black and white editorial fashion photo. Creates an image of a person in a dynamic crouched pose against a white backdrop, wearing all-black clothing and sunglasses, with a wide-angle camera perspective.

AI prompt for creating ultra-realistic fashion portraits with faux fur coats and bear cubs. Uses identity lock to preserve facial features from reference photos. Professional studio photography style.

A detailed prompt to generate a realistic street portrait using your uploaded photo. Creates a sharp, still subject against a motion-blurred, crowded city background with professional DSLR photo quality.

Generate a powerful, cinematic portrait from your photo. This prompt creates a low-angle shot with a single beam of light cutting across the face, resulting in a dramatic, heroic silhouette against a dark background.

AI prompt creates realistic cafe portraits from your reference photo. Includes detailed clothing textures, cinematic lighting, and urban atmosphere. Perfect for fashion portraits and personal photos in 9:16 vertical format.

AI prompt creates dramatic professional portraits with crimson backgrounds using your reference photo. Features cinematic lighting, intense contrast, and sleek black suit. Perfect for business headshots in 1080x1920 vertical format.

AI prompt creates professional editorial fashion portraits with top-down perspective using your reference photo. Features seamless gradient background, circular spotlight lighting, and wide-angle lens effect in 9:16 vertical format.

An AI prompt for a hyperrealistic, full-body studio portrait featuring atmospheric smoke and warm amber lighting. Transforms your photo into a cinematic, fashion-editorial scene with a seated pose and dramatic light rays.

Ultra-realistic 8K high-fashion studio portrait preserving your exact face, olive skin, and athletic build. Waist-up, charcoal pinstripe suit, burgundy tie, gold tie bar, neck and finger tattoos, toothpick in hand. Cinematic lighting, deep burgundy background, modern mafia aesthetic, 9:16.

Luxury fashion editorial triptych preserving your exact face with zero alteration. Three vertical frames: hand near mouth, head tilt with hand on forehead, ring near lips. Black swept-back hair, white shirt, black vest, hand tattoo, statement ring. Soft studio lighting, muted grey background, cinematic realism, 9:16.
